headline.print_headline: Away Wins for Barca and PSG in Champions League Last 16
headline.main: Away Wins for Barca and PSG in Champions League Last 16

lead_paragraph: Barcelona and Paris St Germain claimed impressive victories at Manchester City and Bayer Leverkusen respectively in the first legs of their Champions League last 16 ties on Tuesday.
